Subject: [PATCH 2/4] ADD reviewed-patch feature-done prompts so completed work
 requires a decision

Prompt the reviewed patch-agent chat after clean review so the user explicitly closes or reopens the feature before linearization. Keep yes/no answers local to the controller, reopen non-answer follow-up input through the normal agent path, and highlight the pending decision in the terminal so reviewed work is visible.
